name: Rare Floogull
description: Rare Floogull posits that the most mouthwatering meal is one that belongs to someone else! This renegade Rare quietly hovers in the vicinity of feasts, brunches, and midnight snackings in order to swipe a stray morsel. When scolded, the beaked bandit is quick to make amends with an apologetic honk.
breedingTime: Breeding Time: 1 day 2 hr 30 min, Enhanced Time: 19 hr 52 min 30 sec
